{"tid":756100,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來感情台咁mk","createTime":"2018-07-25T17:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T06:43:46.000Z","uid":58195,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f883f3066eadfe69e3758ee3a4e1a14638baac89","tid":756100,"uid":58195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T17:55:34.000Z","msg":"上左係感情台都耐<br />\n<br />\n流連係感情台睇post<br />\n<br />\n得閒入下神之廢青啲post屌下佢(幾緊)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家先睇到原來係交友台<br />\n<br />\n溝女有<br />\n<br />\n睇起嚟好似做兵嘅都有<br />\n<br />\n我仲以為呢到係毒撚台，大家都係放下負就算<br />\n<br />\n點知原來係mk台<br />\n<br />\n睇嚟毒撚去到邊都係毒撚，做唔到mk <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw仲收唔收毒撚"},{"pid":"bc1fa1022a97724bfca5da09949ac5bd14216be4","tid":756100,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T17:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938f73a7e667c3422df1f22deee2008f687a85f0","tid":756100,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T17:56:43.000Z","msg":"on9 一早已經係叫5p台"},{"pid":"56c921fbf32e342d33bf660745d5fc7f3617b2aa","tid":756100,"uid":58195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T17:59:04.000Z","msg":"仆街啦<br />\n<br />\n打完真係喊左<br />\n<br />\n原來我比我自己諗仲毒"},{"pid":"6372d8edf2679c2da198fd756c4b933d880ddf49","tid":756100,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T18:00:22.000Z","msg":"mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6008f798189dbc71bde5047a581498900385c4cf","tid":756100,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T18:03:15.